{"tid":485030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【01獨家】呂麗瑤前教練日間指會「請律師」, 晚上攜帶細軟離開住所","createTime":"2017-11-30T15:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T02:34:21.000Z","uid":134071,"like":16,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"b1904812174860440561b572e7fc4724c3b683f3","tid":485030,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:00:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/137865/-01%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6-%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-%E5%91%82%E9%BA%97%E7%91%A4%E5%89%8D%E6%95%99%E7%B7%B4%E6%97%A5%E9%96%93%E5%8F%97%E8%BF%BD%E8%A8%AA-%E6%99%9A%E4%B8%8A%E8%88%87%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E9%9B%A2%E5%AF%93%E6%89%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F137865%2F-01%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2589%2587-%25E5%2591%2582%25E9%25BA%2597%25E7%2591%25A4%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%2595%2599%25E7%25B7%25B4%25E6%2597%25A5%25E9%2596%2593%25E5%258F%2597%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E6%2599%259A%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25AF%2593%25E6%2589%2580&d=3MzjoYWa7%2FEWPGoD32bGPdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=b96b4780\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/137865/-01%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6-%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-%E5%91%82%E9%BA%97%E7%91%A4%E5%89%8D%E6%95%99%E7%B7%B4%E6%97%A5%E9%96%93%E5%8F%97%E8%BF%BD%E8%A8%AA-%E6%99%9A%E4%B8%8A%E8%88%87%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E9%9B%A2%E5%AF%93%E6%89%80</a></span><br />\n<br />\n 港聞<br />\n【01獨家．有片】呂麗瑤前教練日間受追訪　晚上與家人離寓所<br />\n撰文： 香港01記者<br />\n發佈日期：2017-11-30 22:40<br />\n最後更新日期：2017-11-30 22:42<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「香港欄后」呂麗瑤今日（30日）凌晨在facebook發帖指，自己於初中時曾被教練性侵犯，轟動全港。呂麗瑤的現任教練鄧漢昇早上接受電台訪問後，<strong>《香港01》記者曾於下午找到呂麗瑤其中一位前教練，詢問他對事件的看法，當時這位前教練指「唔想講嘢」及「驚講錯到時麻煩，要請律師先。」至晚上，《香港01》記者則見他與家人離開大埔寓所，坐的士往青衣。</strong><br />\n<br />\n家人主動走近　稱一家外出晚飯<br />\n<br />\n記者從下午訪問這位前教練後，一直在其大埔的住所外等候，期間他不時走出露台觀察。<strong>至晚上7時22分，他與家人離開住所，當時他們攜着兩個背囊及兩個布袋</strong>，其中一位家人主動走近，向記者表示，他們一家外出吃晚飯，又指希望記者不要驚動鄰居。<br />\n<br />\n記者尾隨發現，該名前教練及家人徒步約10分鐘前往大埔富善邨，期間他的家人數次回望記者有否跟隨。他們最後登上的士，前往青衣，至晚上約8時，他與家人在青衣港鐵站下車，進入站內並失去影踪。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《香港01》記者於下午，曾向這位前教練問及對事件的看法，他起初指「唔想講嘢」，及後指「驚講錯到時麻煩，要請律師先」，再問及其他問題時，他則稱「唔清楚」、「唔知」。</strong>"},{"pid":"b4d1932a9c6d753b56f32d87b270ca218e0810f0","tid":485030,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d461d8a0714ab6bbb84c7d09e299c4c3ac9aff37","tid":485030,"uid":155818,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:01:49.000Z","msg":"01好癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0d6db149a40c227c029ca494d77fffdfbac3be","tid":485030,"uid":22858,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>經crosscheck多個post，最新確信五毛名單臚列如下：<br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: red;\">三色貓</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">法國佬巫斯義</span></del>、<del><span style=\"